_sText:
Created for the Treasure Hunter Mapping Contest.

A deserted city of ruins in the jungle is about to be destroyed by terrorists, unless CT's can manage to stop them in time...

Fight through ancient ruins and jungle under a late afternoon sky and the glow of fire.

The map holds up to 32 people. 

*************************
Currently been having troubles with the radar. This version does not contain it. If I'm able to figure out the problem I will update this.
